CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1953, pg. 27, reads: "Novice Swim Meet - The City Recreation Department held its annual novice swimming meet last Thursday at Moore Pool in Brookline... John Brown, right, shown with his coach, Ammon Pool headguard Terence Garmon, won two events to help his team pile up 55 points to finish second to the Arlington squad. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Swimmer John Brown and coach Terence Garmon, walking near edge of swimming pool, for City Recreation Department swim meet, at Moore Pool, Brookline
